00:34:54.679 --> 00:34:56.512
for women, we're at a
turning point for men.

00:34:56.512 --> 00:34:59.360
And I talk quite a bit about
the idea of sacred masculinity

00:34:59.360 --> 00:35:01.300
and modeling good
