00:36:20.790 --> 00:36:23.670
And I was wondering
what, in your view,

00:36:23.670 --> 00:36:28.370
a feminine model of leadership
or a gender neutral model

00:36:28.370 --> 00:36:29.780
of leadership would look like?

00:36:29.780 --> 00:36:30.920
ELIZABETH CRONISE MCLAUGHLIN:
